"><div class="media-object-video"><div class="wsj-media-summary clearfix"><div class="strap-container"><h4 class="strap" itemprop="description"></h4></div></div><iframe width="400" height="225" src="https://video-api.wsj.com/api-video/player/v3/iframe.html?guid=0836B1C8-90CB-46AD-B682-0CABB3C8C207&amp;height=225&amp;width=400&amp;plid=video_amp&amp;chainVideos=true&amp;parentUrl=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Famp%2Farticles%2Fdonald-trump-indictment-documents-mar-a-lago-security-footage-carlos-de-oliveira-walt-nauta-a0061873&amp;a=a" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></iframe><p class="imageCaption"> 2023 年 6 月 11 日，前司法部长威廉·巴尔在接受“福克斯周日新闻”采访时否认了有关唐纳德·特朗普的起诉是困扰其总统任期的“政治迫害”的延续的说法。图片：美联社/法新社/盖蒂图片社 综合：马克·凯利<span class="imageCredit">华尔街日报互动版</span></p></div></div></section></div></main></div>]]>;</description><pubDate> Fri, 28 Jul 2023 22:20:00 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://www.wsj.com/articles/donald-trump-indictment-documents-mar-a-lago-security-footage-carlos-de-oliveira-walt-nauta-a0061873</guid><link/> https://www.wsj.com/articles/donald-trump-indictment-documents-mar-a-lago-security-footage-carlos-de-oliveira-walt-nauta-a0061873<author><![CDATA[The Editorial Board]]></author><category>企业犯罪/法律诉讼</category><category>企业/行业新闻</category><category>法律诉讼 - 高管</category><category>政治/一般新闻</category><category>犯罪/法律诉讼</category><category>政治/国际关系</category><category>国内政治</category><category>内容类型</category><category>评论/意见</category><category>法激活过滤器</category><category>C&amp;E 行政新闻过滤器</category><category>会展行业新闻过滤器</category><category>SYND</category><category>华尔街日报-PRO-WSJ.com</category><category>卡洛斯·德·奥利维拉</category><category>沃尔特·诺塔</category><category>唐纳德·特朗普</category><category>企业犯罪</category><category>合法举动</category><category>公司的</category><category>行业新闻</category><category>法律诉讼 - 高管</category><category>政治的</category><category>一般新闻</category><category>犯罪</category><category>政治</category><category>国际关系</category><category>国内政治</category><category>内容类型</category><catego